      • update

        public void update()
        Reads (updated) JNA Memory and modifies values in list. This must be called after native PKCS#11 calls in Native that modify CK_ATTRIBUTE struct such as Native.C_GetAttributeValue(NativeLong, NativeLong, Template, NativeLong). This is automatically done by the Wrapper and EnhancedWrapper interfaces.
